WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:08.000
<v Thomas Renneberg>Good morning everyone, let's review the risk register for Drop 2.</v>

2
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:18.000
<v Sarah Chen>We identified a new risk around the model validation dataset. The sample size may be insufficient for the intended use population.</v>

3
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:28.000
<v Thomas Renneberg>That's a significant concern. Can we quantify the impact on our regulatory submission timeline?</v>

4
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:40.000
<v Sarah Chen>If we need to collect additional data, it could delay the submission by four to six weeks. I recommend we create a risk item and start the mitigation planning now.</v>
